This paper deals with data structures (Bloom filters) and algorithms for sampling and reconstruction, which are topics typically studied in computer science sub-categories such as data structures (cs.DS), databases (cs.DB), cryptography (cs.CR), information theory (cs.IT), and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
